(b) If left unattended for more than twenty-four hours on
any public property, except a portion thereof on which parking is legally
permitted;

(c) If left unattended for more than forty-eight hours, after
the parking of such vehicle has become illegal, if left on a portion of any
public property on which parking is legally permitted;

(d) If left unattended for more than seven days on private
property if left initially without permission of the owner, or after permission
